{"data":{"id":"https://worldcouncilforhealth.substack.com/p/epidemiologist-drops-bombshell-evidence","title":"Epidemiologist Drops Bombshell Evidence: Why Covid mRNA Shots Must Be Banned","link":"https://worldcouncilforhealth.substack.com/p/epidemiologist-drops-bombshell-evidence","pubDate":"Wed, 19 Feb 2025 16:28:29 GMT","description":"17 million lives at stake: the undeniable case for an mRNA injection moratorium","content":"<div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0de958a2-9a50-4fed-a59d-168aee17bf72_900x473.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0de958a2-9a50-4fed-a59d-168aee17bf72_900x473.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0de958a2-9a50-4fed-a59d-168aee17bf72_900x473.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0de958a2-9a50-4fed-a59d-168aee17bf72_900x473.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0de958a2-9a50-4fed-a59d-168aee17bf72_900x473.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0de958a2-9a50-4fed-a59d-168aee17bf72_900x473.jpeg\" width=\"900\" height=\"47